South African female boxing champion Leighandre ‘Baby Lee’ Jegels has been killed in a shooting incident near Mdantsane in East London. Jegels’ mother was also shot and is in hospital. The shooting took place following a high speed car chase. It is alleged that the shooter, her boyfriend, is a member of the South African Police Service. Police have confirmed that the Independent Police Investigative Directorate (IPID) is investigating a case against the boxer’s policeman boyfriend.